{"tid":339261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港潛在私樓供應量   9.8萬伙創新高","createTime":"2017-07-29T02:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T03:01:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c85773d378645973477b7e02810d9c6e8c328d","tid":339261,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1865000/1867868/cvvn20170625105_01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1865000%2F1867868%2Fcvvn20170625105_01_600.jpg&h=e8603369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局公布，第二季私人住宅施工量為6000伙，按季增1.4倍；同期落成量4400伙，與上季相同，但按年減少21%。數字顯示，未來三至四年私樓的潛在供應量，達9.8萬伙新高，比首季多2000伙，連續三個季度增長。<br />\n<br />\n當中8000伙是已落成但未出售的單位，而建築中但仍未出售的單位就有6.1萬伙，兩組數字與上季相同。已批出但未動工的「熟地」，可提供2.9萬伙，按季增加7.4%。"},{"pid":"fc89f757f30735ec41091df9518eb642f3c91680","tid":339261,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170728/photo/bkn-20170728093750185-0728_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170729084217\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170728%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170728093750185-0728_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170729084217&h=0f7b1b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170728/photo/bkn-20170728093750185-0728_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170729084217\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170728%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170728093750185-0728_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170729084217&h=8e5e7e7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be98f764debcc75919f5af9865bdb383483342b9","tid":339261,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:01:00.000Z","msg":"Nice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /